source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000010_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Nald, keeper of the realm of the living.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000010_NALDTHAL<tab>Je suis Nald, et je règne sur la vie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000020_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Thal, keeper of the realm of the dead.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000020_NALDTHAL<tab>Je suis Thal... Je règne sur la mort...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000025_NALDTHAL<tab>Prepare to be judged, children of man.

TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000040_ENDSINGER_NONE_VOICEHope, is it...? Futile. Utterly futile.
Such feeble light is powerless before darkest despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000040_ENDSINGER_NONE_VOICE<tab>Une prière...<var 1D /var>? Croyez-vous sincèrement que votre frêle flambeau d'espoir soit capable de percer la noirceur qui règne en ce lieu<var 1D /var>!? Jamais<var 1D /var>!
